---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>AmicBridge – Borrow, Lend & Financial Request Platform</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="AmicBridge is a Cyprus-based peer-to-peer request platform that helps connect borrowers and lenders. Users submit structured loan or lending requests, and AmicBridge assists in matching compatible profiles with transparency and clear risk awareness."
    />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  </head>

  <body class="page">
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
        <div class="logo">
          <span class="logo-mark">A</span>
          <span class="logo-text">AmicBridge</span>
        </div>

        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="#mission" class="nav-link">Mission</a>
          <a href="#how" class="nav-link">How it works</a>
          <a href="#trust" class="nav-link">Trust principles</a>
          <a href="#borrow" class="nav-link">Borrow</a>
          <a href="#lend" class="nav-link">Lend</a>
          <a href="#strategy" class="nav-link">Strategy</a>
          <a href="#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1 class="hero-title">Peer-to-peer lending requests with transparency and responsible communication.</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            AmicBridge is a Cyprus-based platform that helps individuals request a loan,
            offer to lend, or ask for investment strategy guidance. We stand in the middle,
            review submissions for clarity, and seek to match compatible profiles.
            Transfers and agreements happen directly between users.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="#borrow" class="btn btn-primary">Request a loan</a>
            <a href="#lend" class="btn btn-secondary">Offer to lend</a>
          </div>

          <p class="hero-note">
            Important: AmicBridge does not hold funds, transfer money, or guarantee any match,
            loan, profit or result. Borrowing, lending and investing always carry risk, and
            users must make decisions independently.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MISSION -->
    <section id="mission" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Mission & background</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          AmicBridge was created to improve clarity in peer-to-peer lending.
          Borrowers often struggle to explain their needs. Lenders often lack structured,
          comparable information. We reduce the noise by collecting requests using the same format,
          encouraging transparency and responsible risk awareness.
        </p>

        <ul class="bridge-list">
          <li>Cyprus-based peer-to-peer request platform</li>
          <li>Structured forms for borrowing, lending, and strategy requests</li>
          <li>No holding of user funds, wallets, or private keys</li>
          <li>No guaranteed outcomes or matches</li>
          <li>Users handle transfers directly between themselves</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
    <section id="how" class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">How AmicBridge works</h2>
        <div class="how-grid">
          <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-number">1</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Users submit requests</h3>
              <p>
                Borrowers, lenders and strategy clients fill out structured forms,
                describing terms, amounts, goals and relevant details.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-number">2</span>
            <div>
              <h3>We review submissions</h3>
              <p>
                We examine whether requests are clear, internally consistent, and
                traceable to basic identity data. This reduces anonymous or incoherent requests.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-number">3</span>
            <div>
              <h3>We help align compatible profiles</h3>
              <p>
                Where possible, we assist in connecting users whose terms match:
                amount, asset type, time period, interest expectation, and purpose.
                We do not move money or guarantee matches.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRUST PRINCIPLES -->
    <section id="trust" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Trust, responsibility & principles</h2>

        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="principle-card">
            <h3>Transparency first</h3>
            <p>
              Requests are structured, not vague. We encourage clear explanations
              so both sides can make informed decisions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle-card">
            <h3>Identity context</h3>
            <p>
              We request essential identity details. This does not guarantee a user's
              financial quality but improves clarity and reduces anonymous misuse.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle-card">
            <h3>Risk awareness</h3>
            <p>
              Lending, borrowing and investing always carry risk. Defaults can happen.
              Market changes can impact outcomes — especially with crypto.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle-card">
            <h3>No fund custody</h3>
            <p>
              AmicBridge does not hold money, crypto, or private keys.
              Transfers happen directly between the people involved.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BORROW -->
    <section id="borrow" class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Request a loan</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          Submit details about how much you need, why, how long, and what repayment terms you can accept.
          You may request cash via bank transfer or crypto.
        </p>

        <form class="form">
          <label>
            Full name
            <input type="text" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Email
            <input type="email" required />
          </label>

          <div class="form-row">
            <label>
              Amount needed
              <input type="number" min="1" required placeholder="Example: 10000" />
            </label>

            <label>
              Currency / asset
              <select>
                <option>EUR (bank)</option>
                <option>USD (bank)</option>
                <option>NOK (bank)</option>
                <option>BTC (crypto)</option>
                <option>ETH (crypto)</option>
                <option>USDT (crypto)</option>
              </select>
            </label>
          </div>

          <label>
            Duration
            <select>
              <option>Up to 6 months</option>
              <option>Up to 12 months</option>
              <option>Up to 24 months</option>
              <option>Up to 36 months</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label>
            Max annual interest you can accept
            <input type="number" min="1" max="40" placeholder="Example: 10%" />
          </label>

          <label>
            Purpose of the loan
            <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Describe your reason and repayment plan"></textarea>
          </label>

          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Submit loan request</button>

          <p class="card-note">
            This submission does not create an agreement. Lenders decide independently.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LEND -->
    <section id="lend" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Offer to lend</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          Share how much you want to lend, desired return, and what kind of borrowers you prefer.
          Cash or crypto can be offered.
        </p>

        <form class="form">
          <label>
            Full name
            <input type="text" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Email
            <input type="email" required />
          </label>

          <div class="form-row">
            <label>
              Amount to lend
              <input type="number" min="1" placeholder="Example: 5000" required />
            </label>

            <label>
              Currency / asset
              <select>
                <option>EUR (bank)</option>
                <option>USD (bank)</option>
                <option>NOK (bank)</option>
                <option>BTC (crypto)</option>
                <option>ETH (crypto)</option>
                <option>USDT (crypto)</option>
              </select>
            </label>
          </div>

          <label>
            Target annual interest
            <input type="number" min="1" max="40" placeholder="Example: 8%" />
          </label>

          <label>
            Preferred borrower profile
            <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Example: private persons, business owners, etc."></textarea>
          </label>

          <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-full">Submit lending profile</button>

          <p class="card-note">
            Lending involves risk. Borrowers may fail to repay.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STRATEGY -->
    <section id="strategy" class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Investment strategy request</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          Describe your goals and budget to request investment strategy ideas.
          This may include traditional assets or crypto.
        </p>

        <form class="form">
          <label>
            Full name
            <input type="text" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Email
            <input type="email" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Budget for strategy service (EUR equivalent)
            <input type="number" min="1" placeholder="Example: 200" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Describe your goal
            <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Long-term growth, retirement, savings, etc."></textarea>
          </label>

          <label>
            What can you invest in?
            <textarea rows="2" placeholder="Stocks, funds, crypto, cash, etc."></textarea>
          </label>

          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Submit request</button>

          <p class="card-note">
            Any ideas received are not guaranteed outcomes. Finance and markets can move in both directions.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTACT -->
    <section id="contact" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Contact & responsibility</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          AmicBridge operates from Cyprus and supports responsible, transparent peer-to-peer communication.
          For questions, concerns or business inquiries, contact the founder directly.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-card">
          <p><strong>CEO:</strong> Robert</p>
          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong>
            <a href="mailto:Robertamicolsen@gmail.com">Robertamicolsen@gmail.com</a>
          </p>
          <p class="contact-note">
            Please avoid sending sensitive data (passwords, private keys, etc.)
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LEGAL NOTICE -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <p class="footer-main">
          AmicBridge is a Cyprus-based peer-to-peer request platform.
          It does not act as a bank, custodian, broker or financial advisor, and does not
          hold user funds. All agreements and transfers occur directly between users,
          who must evaluate risk and legality themselves.
        </p>
        <p class="footer-meta">© {year} AmicBridge · Responsible transparency matters.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>

  <style>
    /* GLOBAL */
    :global(body) {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: #f6f7fa;
      color: #1e1e1e;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* LAYOUT */
    .container {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .section-alt {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-block: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .section-lead {
      max-width: 50rem;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    .header {
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
    }

    .header-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #3b82f6, #6366f1);
      color: white;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #444;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      transition: color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .nav-link:hover {
      color: #000;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
      background: #fafbfe;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 830px;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #4b5563;
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero-note {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #666;
      max-width: 30rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* BUTTONS */
    .btn {
      border-radius: 0.45rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #6366f1, #3b82f6);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4f46e5, #2563eb);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      border-color: #d0d3da;
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #222;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f1f2f5;
      border-color: #babec7;
    }

    .btn-full {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
    }

    /* INFO LISTS */
    .bridge-list, .principles-grid {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .bridge-list li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #3b3b3b;
    }

    .principles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }

    .principle-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e4e6eb;
      border-radius: 0.8rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 1rem;
    }

    /* HOW GRID */
    .how-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }

    .how-step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .how-number {
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #eef0ff;
      border: 1px solid #c7ccf7;
      color: #3f4cd0;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    /* FORMS */
    .form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 0.9rem;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #555;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }

    input, select, textarea {
      border-radius: 0.4rem;
      border: 1px solid #d2d5dc;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
      font: inherit;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.12s ease;
    }

    input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
      border-color: #6366f1;
    }

    .form-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .contact-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 0.8rem;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      max-width: 420px;
    }

    .contact-card a {
      color: #4755f1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    .footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: #505050;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-main {
      max-width: 40rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    @media(max-width: 900px) {
      .principles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
      .how-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media(max-width: 700px) {
      .form, .contact-card {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }

  </style>
</html>
